Closing on: 9 May 2022 Job Type: Fixed-term contract, with possibility of permanent employment Job Location: Based in Johannesburg We are looking for a sales representative who can take charge of our subscription business and develop corporate packages to increase our subscriber base. The ideal candidate also has experience selling investor relations packages and creating new audiences for the company. They will need to be a problem solver, solutions provider and value creator, with a minimum of five years sales experience gained in the media. They will have a passion for sales and advertising and have a proven ability to create sales opportunities and business. Developing new business must be a passion and strong relationships with key decision-makers is vital. Main responsibilities: Requirements: All interested applicants are requested to apply with a comprehensive CV to the Operations Director Mosehla Tsebe by email on mosehla@moneyweb.co.za. Moneyweb is an equal opportunity employer and will give preference to applications from the designated groups. Applicants not contacted by 12 May 2022 should consider their applications unsuccessful.